The paper discusses the role of scientific competitions in robotics, specifically in the field of service robotics. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in robotics competitions and the importance of integrating robots into society (cs.HC). The paper also mentions challenges in taking robots to people's homes, which could fall under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the collection of data for further research, which could involve computer vision (cs.CV).
